responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "BD07B1FA495B6912FA57838A549F896F", "Do you have a knack with a hammer? I find myself in a pickle. My wheel got trapped in a rut in the road and I\'ve snapped the axle. I\'m more of a business man than a mechanic, though, I don\'t have the faintest idea how to make the repair. Could you help?")
